It's a dressing table... Actually, I don't use it much.

I randomly placed these flowers... Somehow, I feel like they
are growing.
There are several identical white dresses in the closet.

I bought these flowers to match with Lunaroa. But... I feel
like I'm going to make them wither before her.

I impulsively bought a balance at the store. Because... it's
cool, you know... But... it's quite annoying swaying around.
